libgltf
------------------------------------------
LIBGLTF is a C++ library for rendering OpenGL models stored in glTF format.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.6-1
  libepoxy-devel-1.4.3-1
  libepoxy0-1.4.3-1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libgltf0.1-devel-0.1.0-1bl2
  libgltf0.1_1-0.1.0-1bl2
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  pkg-config-2.3.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-2
  automake-20240607-1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  glm-devel-0.9.9.5-1
  libboost-devel-1.66.0-1
  libepoxy-devel-1.4.3-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://www.libreoffice.org

Canonical download:
  https://dev-www.libreoffice.org/src/libgltf/libgltf-0.1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libgltf-0.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libgltf-0.1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libgltf-0.1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgltf-0.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgltf0.1_1-0.1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libgltf0.1-devel-0.1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libgltf)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libgltf.README
  /usr/share/doc/libgltf/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libgltf/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libgltf/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libgltf/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libgltf/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libgltf/README

(libgltf0.1_1)
  /usr/bin/cyggltf-0.1-1.dll

(libgltf0.1-devel)
  /usr/include/libgltf-0.1/libgltf.h
  /usr/include/libgltf-0.1/types.h
  /usr/lib/libgltf-0.1.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libgltf-0.1.pc

